Package com.jwetherell.algorithms.data_structures

Class Graph<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
com.jwetherell.algorithms.data_structures.Graph<T>
public class Graph<T extends Comparable<T>> extends Object
Graph. Could be directed or undirected depending on the TYPE enum. A graph is an abstract representation of a set of objects where some pairs of the objects are connected by links.

Author:
Justin Wetherell <phishman3579@gmail.com>
